<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Onboarding Prototype — AutoPayPlus</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #F4F6F8; color: #1A1A2E; }

    /* ── Header ── */
    .site-header { background: #0C3A5E; padding: 14px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .site-header h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
    .site-header span { color: #7BAFD4; font-size: 13px; }

    /* ── Layout ── */
    .main { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; min-height: calc(100vh - 52px); }

    /* ── Column headers ── */
    .col-header {
      padding: 16px 20px 10px;
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    .col-header.existing { background: rgba(248,249,252,.97); border-bottom: 3px solid #6B7280; }
    .col-header.proposed { background: rgba(239,246,255,.97); border-bottom: 3px solid #0576CE; }
    .col-header .eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .col-header.existing .eyebrow { color: #6B7280; }
    .col-header.proposed .eyebrow { color: #0576CE; }
    .col-header h2 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
    .col-header p { font-size: 11px; color: #6B7280; margin-top: 2px; }

    /* ── Columns ── */
    .col { padding: 12px 16px 32px; }
    .col.existing { background: #F8F9FC; border-right: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
    .col.proposed { background: #EFF6FF; }

    /* ── Phase headings ── */
    .phase {
      font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #fff; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 3px; display: inline-block;
      margin: 14px 0 6px;
    }
    .phase.dealer  { background: #ea580c; }
    .phase.ops     { background: #7c3aed; }
    .phase.email   { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .phase.sms     { background: #0891b2; }
    .phase.portal  { background: #0576CE; }
    .phase.nudge   { background: #dc2626; }
    .phase.member  { background: #16a34a; }

    /* ── Step cards ── */
    .step {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .step.changed { border-color: #F5A623; background: #FFFBEB; }
    .step.new     { border-color: #0576CE; background: #EFF6FF; }
    .step.removed { opacity: .5; border-style: dashed; }
    .step.highlight { border-color: #16a34a; background: #F0FFF4; }

    .step-num {
      min-width: 30px; height: 30px;
      border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .num-gray   { background: #6B7280; }
    .num-orange { background: #ea580c; }
    .num-blue   { background: #0576CE; }
    .num-purple { background: #7c3aed; }
    .num-teal   { background: #0891b2; }
    .num-green  { background: #16a34a; }
    .num-red    { background: #dc2626; }

    .step-content { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
    .step-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937; }
    .step-desc { font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 2px; line-height: 1.45; }
    .step-badge {
      font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .badge-moved   { background: #FDE68A; color: #92400e; }
    .badge-earlier { background: #D1FAE5; color: #065f46; }
    .badge-new     { background: #DBEAFE; color: #1e40af; }
    .badge-removed { background: #FEE2E2; color: #991b1b; }
    .badge-same    { background: #F3F4F6; color: #374151; }
    .badge-enhanced{ background: #EDE9FE; color: #5b21b6; }

    a.step-link {
      display: inline-block; margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 11px; color: #0576CE; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;
    }
    a.step-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    a.step-link.gray { color: #6B7280; }

    /* ── Divider ── */
    .divider { text-align: center; margin: 8px 0; }
    .divider span { font-size: 10px; color: #9CA3AF; }

    /* ── Portal cards section ── */
    .portals-section { grid-column: 1 / -1; padding: 20px 20px 32px; background: #0C3A5E; }
    .portals-section h3 { color: #fff; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .portals { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; }
    a.portal-card {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
      text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px;
      transition: box-shadow .15s, opacity .15s;
    }
    a.portal-card:hover { opacity: .9; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.3); }
    .pc-left { flex: 1; }
    .pc-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; }
    .pc-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
    .pc-desc { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); margin-top: 2px; }
    .pc-icon svg { color: #fff; opacity: .85; }

    /* ── Legend ── */
    .legend { grid-column: 1 / -1; padding: 12px 20px; background: #F8F9FC; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .leg-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-size: 11px; color: #374151; }
    .leg-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 2px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="site-header">
    <h1>AutoPayPlus — Onboarding Prototype</h1>
    <span>|</span>
    <span>Existing Flow vs Proposed Flow</span>
  </div>

  <!-- ── LEGEND ── -->
  <div class="legend">
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#FDE68A;border:1px solid #F5A623"></div> Order moved</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#D1FAE5;border:1px solid #16a34a"></div> Fires earlier</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#DBEAFE;border:1px solid #0576CE"></div> New step</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#EDE9FE;border:1px solid #7c3aed"></div> Enhanced</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#F3F4F6;border:1px solid #D1D5DB"></div> Same / no change</div>
    <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#FEE2E2;border:1px solid #dc2626;opacity:.5"></div> Proposed removal</div>
  </div>

  <div class="main">

    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- LEFT: EXISTING CARL'S FLOW                 -->
    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div>
      <div class="col-header existing">
        <div class="eyebrow">Current State</div>
        <h2>Existing Onboarding Flow</h2>
        <p>Carl's documented sequence — Steps 1–19 · Source: CRM / Creatio</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col existing">

        <div class="phase dealer">At Dealer</div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-orange">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">E-Sign SMS — Verification Code</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Member receives a bare OTP code from short code 22395. No vehicle name, no context, no link.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-enhanced">Enhanced in proposed</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step1-esign-sms.jpg" target="_blank">View screenshot →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num num-orange">2–6</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Enrollment PDF Viewer</div>
            <div class="step-desc">ACH Debit Agreement · Terms & Conditions · Fee Disclosure · "What Can I Expect?" · Payment Calendar · Trade-in Guarantee Certificate. Signed at dealer via eSig.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">Stays at dealer</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step2to6-enrollment-pdf.pdf" target="_blank">View PDF →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase ops">Operations / Internal</div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num num-purple">8</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">USEA — Lead Missing Info (Auto Email to Dealer)</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Auto-email fires to F&I manager if enrollment form is not received. Asks dealer to fax/email the completed form to orders@autopayplus.com.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">Internal — no change proposed</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step8-dealer-missing-info.html" target="_blank">View email →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num num-purple">9</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Assistance Needed — Enrollment Form Submission</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Internal notification that customer enrollment form has been submitted and needs processing review.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">Internal — no change proposed</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step9-assistance-needed.pdf" target="_blank">View PDF →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase email">Post-Enrollment Emails</div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">11</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">New Member Welcome Email</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"Welcome to AutoPayPlus, Schedule your Welcome Call Today" — from membersupport@autopayplus.com. Generic — no vehicle name, no loan details, no first debit date.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-enhanced">Enhanced + fires earlier in proposed</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step11-welcome-email.html" target="_blank">View email →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">12</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Existing Member — Additional Loan Welcome Email</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"Welcome AGAIN to AutoPayPlus" — fires when an existing member adds a second loan. From DoNotreply@autopayplus.com.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">Existing members only — no change</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step12-additional-loan-welcome.html" target="_blank">View email →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase sms">Welcome SMS (Five9)</div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-teal">13–15</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">CEO Welcome SMS — First Welcome Text</div>
            <div class="step-desc">From Bobby (Robert Steenbergh). Includes welcome call link (Calendly) and member portal login link. Personalized with first name.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-moved">Becomes a nudge / retention trigger in proposed</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num num-teal">16</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">GemCap Welcome Email</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"GemCap Powered by AutoPayPlus!" — From Robert Steenbergh. GemCap-enrolled members only.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">GemCap only — no change</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step16-gemcap-welcome.html" target="_blank">View email →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-teal">17</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">48hrs — Welcome Security Link (Magic Link Email)</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"Welcome to AutoPayPlus!" from membersupport. Contains the magic link to authenticate and complete portal setup. Fires 48 hours after enrollment.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-earlier">Fires immediately in proposed (Day 0)</div>
            <a class="step-link gray" href="/steps/step17-security-link.html" target="_blank">View email →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase nudge">Non-Login Nudge Sequence</div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-red">18</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">2nd Welcome SMS — Not Yet Logged In</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"We noticed you have not logged into your Members' Portal account yet." Includes re-auth security link and steps to complete setup.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">Still needed — timing may adjust</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-red">19</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">3rd Welcome SMS — Open Enrollment Pitch</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"AutoPayPlus is thrilled to help you..." 6-month open enrollment window, no-fee loan additions, Calendly link.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">Still needed — cadence may adjust</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div><!-- /col existing -->
    </div>

    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- RIGHT: PROPOSED FLOW                       -->
    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div>
      <div class="col-header proposed">
        <div class="eyebrow">Proposed — Prospect Portal (First Steps)</div>
        <h2>New Member Onboarding Flow</h2>
        <p>Brad/Chris prototype · chrislocality.com/apponboarding · 18 screens</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col proposed">

        <div class="phase dealer">At Dealer (same timing)</div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-orange">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">E-Sign SMS — Personalized Enrollment Trigger</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Vehicle name + member first name + magic link + "~5 min" estimate. Fires the moment dealer taps Enroll — not just an OTP code.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-enhanced">Enhanced from bare OTP → personalized CTA</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/00-sms-enrollment.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step highlight">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">E1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Welcome Email — Loan at a Glance</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Vehicle name + loan amount + APR + term + "Set Up My Account →" CTA. "Link expires in 7 days." Fires same day — not 48 hours later.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-earlier">Step 17 moved from Day+2 to Day 0</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/email-01-welcome.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase portal">Prospect Portal — First Steps</div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Magic Link Landing — Value + No Surprises</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Loan data pre-filled. Interest savings hook above fold. "No surprises, nothing hidden." First screen after member taps the SMS/email link.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New screen — replaces blank portal entry</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/01-magic-link.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Identity Verification — DOB or Last 4 SSN</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Member chooses path. Encryption callout inline. FullStory: 4,903 enter · 16.4% convert — #1 drop-off.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New — replaces unstructured auth entry</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/02-identity.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Choose MFA — Text or Email</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Two delivery channels. "Use a different method" escape hatch visible.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/03-choose-mfa.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">04</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Enter MFA — 6-Digit Code</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Auto-advance input. Resend + method switch both available. "Secure and encrypted" footer.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/04-enter-mfa.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">05</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Confirm Contact Details</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Pre-filled from Creatio. Member corrects if needed. "Nothing else" trust micro-copy.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/05-confirm-contact.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/05-confirm-contact-errors.html" target="_blank">View error states →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">06</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Create Login — Password + Credentials</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Real-time 4-criterion password validation. Show/hide toggle. "Bank-level security" badge.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/06-create-login.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">07</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Add Debit Method — ACH Banking Info</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"Debit method" terminology. First debit timing explained before any data entry. "Skip for now" with downstream orange warning.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">Moves part of Steps 2–6 online</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/07-payment-method.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">08</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">TransUnion — Credit Monitoring Method Select</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"Included Benefit · No cost to you." Text / Voice / Security Questions. 83% who reach TU complete it (FullStory). ⚠️ Position ON HOLD per April 9.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New — credit benefit framed as reward</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/08-transunion-method.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">9a</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">TransUnion OTP — Enter 6-Digit Code</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"Use a different method" escape visible. "Having trouble? Get help" links to Get Help screen.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/09a-transunion-otp.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">9b</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">TransUnion KBA — Security Questions</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"A few questions to verify you." One question at a time. Radio buttons. "Choose a different method" escape.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/09b-transunion-kba.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">10</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Credit Score Reveal — Milestone Screen</div>
            <div class="step-desc">"Your credit monitoring is on." Score + rating shown. "No impact to your score" inline. Cross-sell insurance introduced as Optional.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New — TU as earned milestone</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/10-credit-score.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step new">
          <div class="step-num num-blue">11</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Setup Summary — Checklist Receipt</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Done / Needed / Optional. Orange warning ×2 if debit method skipped. Insurance cross-sell as Optional. "Skip to dashboard" secondary.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New — completion + cross-sell in one screen</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/11-setup-summary.html" target="_blank">View prototype →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase member">Member Portal — Post-Activation</div>

        <div class="step highlight">
          <div class="step-num num-green">12</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Dashboard — Single or Multi-Loan</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Next debit date + amount. Progress bar. "3 loans on track" badge. 5-tab nav: Dashboard · Accounts · Credit · Service · More.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-same">Hands off to Jeff/dev team portal project</div>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/12-dashboard.html" target="_blank">Single loan →</a>
            <a class="step-link" href="/draft2/12-dashboard-multi.html" target="_blank">Multi-loan →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase nudge">Nudge Sequence (Non-Activated)</div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-red">N1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">48hr Nudge — No Portal Login (was Step 17–18)</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Magic link re-send + reminder. Targets members who received enrollment SMS/email but haven't authenticated. Current Step 17 re-purposed.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-moved">Steps 17–18 consolidated into a triggered nudge</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step changed">
          <div class="step-num num-red">N2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">72hr SMS — Open Enrollment Reminder (was Step 19)</div>
            <div class="step-desc">6-month open enrollment window. No-fee additional loan adds. Calendly link for welcome call.</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-moved">Step 19 re-timed to Day 3 trigger</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num num-teal">?</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Get Help — Available at Any Step</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Linked from TU + any step in the funnel. Call / Text / Email / Book 15-min. "Your progress is saved — back to where I was."</div>
            <div class="step-badge badge-new">New — replaces dead-end drop-offs</div>
